PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Benedict J. Kuzmicz, of Candiac, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Canada Ports Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Brian Keple, whose term has expired.
